---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Impressum — Return to Breath" description="Legal information for returntobreath.net." lang="en">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-32 pb-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 leading-tight mb-10">Impressum.</h1>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">Site Operator</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      <p><strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Christoph Kneip</strong><br />Butzenstrasse 130<br />8041 Zürich<br />Switzerland</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@returnapp.org" class="text-sapphire-400 hover:text-sapphire-300 transition-colors">info@returnapp.org</a></p>
      <p>Jurisdiction: Zürich, Switzerland</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">Health Disclaimer</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      The information on this website is offered for educational and informational purposes only. It is not medical or psychological advice. Conscious breathing practices may be contraindicated for certain conditions including pregnancy, cardiovascular disease, severe respiratory conditions, and panic disorder under active treatment. Consult a qualified healthcare professional before beginning.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">Copyright</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      All content © 2026 Christoph Kneip. Quotation under fair use, with attribution, is welcomed.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">Data Protection</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      Newsletter emails are processed by Buttondown on the basis of consent. Unsubscribe with one click. No analytics or cookies beyond those strictly necessary.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">Applicable Law</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
      Governed by the law of Switzerland. Place of jurisdiction: Zürich.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
